optical constants server

Hello, I am a small webserver serving you optical constants of elements and
some compounds.

The data are taken from IMD.


http://server:port/E        -- outputs complete .nk-file of element E
http://server:port/E/0.155  -- outputs 1 - delta + beta i of element E at wavelength 0.155 nm
http://server:port/E/8000eV -- outputs 1 - delta + beta i of element E at energy 8000 eV
http://server:port/E/8keV   -- outputs 1 - delta + beta i of element E at energy 8 keV


Written by Markus Osterhoff, osterhof@esrf.eu.

Using mongoose -- http://code.google.com/p/mongoose/

